<div class="jumbotron text-center">
  <h1>BIENVENUE SUR RESTAUCONNECT</h1>
  <p>L'uniers des restaurants et des commandes de vos boufs</p>
  <% if user_signed_in? %>
    <%= link_to 'View Your Profile', user_path(current_user), class: 'btn btn-primary btn-lg' %>
    <%= link_to 'Browse Restaurants', restaurants_path, class: 'btn btn-success btn-lg' %>
  <% else %>
    <%= link_to 'Sign Up', new_user_registration_path, class: 'btn btn-primary btn-lg' %>
    <%= link_to 'Log In', new_user_session_path, class: 'btn btn-success btn-lg' %>
  <% end %>
</div>

<div class="container">
  <h2>How It Works</h2>
  <p>RestauConnect helps you find the best deals and meals from top restaurants.</p>
  <ul class="list-unstyled">
    <li><strong>1. Sign Up:</strong> Create an account and explore nearby restaurants.</li>
    <li><strong>2. Browse Menus:</strong> Check out the menus, reviews, and ratings.</li>
    <li><strong>3. Negotiate Prices:</strong> Chat with restaurant owners and get exclusive deals.</li>
    <li><strong>4. Place Your Order:</strong> Order your favorite dishes and enjoy!</li>
  </ul>
</div>
